## Product price (VX) widget

The **Product Price (VX)** displays the available price of the product at the time.

It has three possible states it can display

- Price
- Price and Discount price
- Out of stock

This widget is a quick way to display product price. You can achieve the same result by utilizing dynamic tags and any text based widget, however that will require more work and applying certain conditions, which this widget handles automatically
